Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.16,0:01:35.00,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Are you ready, Shinji?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.36,0:01:36.39,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.39,0:01:38.87,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Release the final safety lock!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.53,0:01:42.34,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Evangelion Unit 01, lift off!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.23,0:01:48.84,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Shinji, just concentrate on\Nwalking right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.40,0:01:50.51,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Walk...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.88,0:02:01.19,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It walked!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.79,0:02:04.86,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Walk...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.83,0:02:16.04,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Shinji, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.50,0:02:18.67,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hurry!  Get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.61,0:02:32.59,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Shinji, calm down!  That’s not your arm!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.55,0:02:38.09,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What’s going on with the Eva’s\Ndefense system?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.09,0:02:39.72,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The signal’s not working!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.72,0:02:41.17,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The field’s not unfolding!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.59,0:02:42.66,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Have we failed?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.70,0:02:48.66,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Left arm damaged!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.66,0:02:49.84,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The circuits have snapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.60,0:02:53.88,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Shinji, dodge!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.94,0:03:01.68,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,There’s a crack on the front\Nof the brain case!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.68,0:03:03.78,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The armor won’t last any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.59,0:03:14.52,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The head’s been damaged!  Extent\Nof damage, unknown!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.52,0:03:16.99,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The control nerves are breaking off!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.99,0:03:19.17,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,We’re not getting any readings\Non the pilot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.83,0:03:20.97,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Shinji!!!
