Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.68,0:04:11.45,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,So, the Angels have returned, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.45,0:04:13.18,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s so sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.18,0:04:15.25,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s the same as it was fifteen years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.25,0:04:19.10,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,A disaster comes as it will,\Nwithout warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.45,0:04:25.43,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,On the positive side, our previous\Ninvestments will not go to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.76,0:04:28.06,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You can’t be sure about that yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.06,0:04:30.53,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,If it doesn’t pay off, it’s a waste\Nall the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.53,0:04:34.42,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Correct.  Now that the Angels have\Nbecome common knowledge...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.42,0:04:37.51,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...we have to manipulate the\Ninformation to avoid trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.51,0:04:43.58,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,NERV must take care of\Nthese matters quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.88,0:04:47.93,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s already been taken care of.\NYou may rest assured of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.08,0:04:53.76,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}In regards to the declaration of the\Nstate of emergency, government\Nofficials have announced...
