Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.63,0:05:02.13,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,So, we’re hushing up the truth again?\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}No, there’s no threat of contamination\Nfrom the center of the explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.13,0:05:02.76,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,But at least our public relations\Npeople are thrilled...\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}No, there’s no threat of contamination\Nfrom the center of the explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.76,0:05:04.00,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,But at least our public relations\Npeople are thrilled...\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}The only Angel samples collected\Nwere adhered to the Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.00,0:05:06.03,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,...now that they’ve finally got\Nsomething to do.\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}The only Angel samples collected\Nwere adhered to the Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.03,0:05:06.54,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,We’re being pretty casual about it.\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}The only Angel samples collected\Nwere adhered to the Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.54,0:05:08.30,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,We’re being pretty casual about it.\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}Correct, as in the model simulation,\Napproximately 99.9% of it evaporated.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.30,0:05:11.47,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,I don’t think so.  Actually, I think\Nwe’re all scared to death.\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}Correct, as in the model simulation,\Napproximately 99.9% of it evaporated.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.47,0:05:12.54,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Correct, as in the model simulation,\Napproximately 99.9% of it evaporated.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.54,0:05:13.99,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Of course we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.58,0:05:16.91,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well, we must acknowledge that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.91,0:05:22.52,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, Mr. Ikari, isn’t there\Na better way to utilize NERV and Eva?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.52,0:05:27.89,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,We’re referring to the repair costs for\NUnit 01, which when added to the\Ncosts for Unit 00...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.89,0:05:29.93,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...are enough to bankrupt\Nan entire country.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.93,0:05:34.50,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,We also understand that you gave that\Nparticular toy to your son, did you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.50,0:05:37.71,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Manpower... time... and money...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.10,0:05:41.17,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,How much more will be wasted by you\Nand your family?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.17,0:05:44.44,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,And that is not your only responsibility.
