Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.44,0:05:46.04,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The Human Instrumentality Project...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.04,0:05:48.51,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...that should be your top priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.51,0:05:49.51,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.51,0:05:55.22,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Under these desperate circumstances,\Nthat project is our only hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.22,0:05:56.79,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.79,0:06:02.17,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,In any case, the Angel is no excuse for\Ndelaying that project’s schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.72,0:06:05.59,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,However, we will consider\Nadjusting the budget.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.59,0:06:08.46,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Now, the rest of this meeting\Nconcerns only us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.46,0:06:10.88,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Your presence here was\Nappreciated, Mr. Ikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.24,0:06:16.81,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Ikari, you do understand there can\Nbe no turning back, don’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.31,0:06:20.98,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.78,0:06:23.88,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Mankind has no time left.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.13,0:06:50.88,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Placement,{\pos(252,404)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Danger
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.17,0:06:56.24,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Air conditioning has just got to be\Nmankind’s greatest treasure.  It’s the\Ntriumph of science over nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.24,0:06:58.58,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Shinji’s woken up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.58,0:07:00.62,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,And... how is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.62,0:07:04.15,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,No external injuries.  His memory is a\Nbit muddled, however.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:06.99,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You don’t think it could\Nbe brain damage?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.99,0:07:09.26,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The doctor said that there was\Nnothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.26,0:07:10.50,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.66,0:07:14.96,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I suppose.  He did have a\Npretty hectic day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.96,0:07:18.74,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,His cranial nerves must have\Ntaken a lot of strain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.10,0:07:21.84,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Don’t you mean... his heart?
