Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.26,0:07:44.49,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Okay, go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.49,0:07:46.17,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yeah, that way.  Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.50,0:07:53.90,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,If Eva and this city both operate at\Ntheir full potential, maybe we can\Nmake it through this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.90,0:07:57.54,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Are you going to defeat the Angels?\NYou’re always such an optimist.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.54,0:08:01.82,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hey, sometimes you need a little wishful\Nthinking just to keep on living.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.78,0:08:07.02,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I see your point.  Your attitude makes\Nme feel a little more at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.05,0:08:08.86,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.63,0:08:11.63,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Placement,{\pos(443,272)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}First Cranial Nerve Division
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.88,0:08:11.25,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Dr. Ugai, Internal\NDepartment 1...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.25,0:08:16.27,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Dr. Ugai, Internal Department 1, please\Ncall Dr. Azuma of the 1st Surgical\NDepartment immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.39,0:08:22.36,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The medical conference on the B\Nexperiment will be held as scheduled.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.36,0:08:25.57,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,All supervisors please proceed to\Nconference room 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.76,0:08:49.46,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:51.16,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,They don’t want to live together?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.16,0:08:56.07,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I think that living apart is natural for\NIkari and his son.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.50,0:09:00.04,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,And being together is unnatural?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.93,0:09:02.02,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Video Edit / Placement,{\pos(101,200)}{\an4}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Residence Registration\N6-24 District-F Geo-Front, Tokyo-3\NIkari Shinji 0001-137-2
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.54,0:09:02.04,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.04,0:09:05.91,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Right.  His room will be in the 6th\Nblock, just beyond this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.91,0:09:07.31,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Is that satisfactory?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.31,0:09:08.48,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.41,0:09:10.95,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.95,0:09:12.21,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Shinji...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.21,0:09:14.39,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s fine.  Being alone is\Nokay with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:17.02,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m alone anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.59,0:09:18.75,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Whaaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.75,0:09:23.17,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,So, I said, I’ll take care of Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.63,0:09:25.30,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’ve already got permission\Nfrom the brass.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.86,0:09:28.70,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hey, it’s not like I’m going to\N“put the moves” on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.70,0:09:29.83,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Of course you’re not!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.83,0:09:32.13,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,How could you even think of\Nsuch a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.13,0:09:32.80,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You’re always like that.  Shame on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.80,0:09:35.18,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,{\c&HFFFFFF&}She just can’t take a joke.\N{\c&H00E3FE&}You’re always like that.  Shame on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.31,0:09:42.25,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well, we’ll have to have a\Nparty tonight, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.34,0:09:44.48,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.48,0:09:47.98,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What for?  A welcoming party for my\Nnew roommate, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.65,0:09:54.76,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Placement,{\pos(421,383)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}100% Beef, Ramen,\NPork-flavor Super Cup, Lawson
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.72,0:09:54.76,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,So, you’re going to move after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.26,0:10:00.70,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yes.  I’d never have dreamt that this city\Nwould become a battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:02.36,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.36,0:10:06.37,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,My husband’s saying that our kid and I\Nshould move, at the very least.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.37,0:10:08.14,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Don’t I know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.14,0:10:12.11,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,This city may be a fortress, but that’s\Nno guarantee of safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.11,0:10:15.55,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Just remembering it gives me the chills.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.68,0:10:17.68,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.12,0:10:24.62,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I hope you don’t mind if we make\Na little stop on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:26.13,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.69,0:10:28.13,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Someplace really cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.23,0:10:37.87,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,So desolate.  This city seems so lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.03,0:10:41.34,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.63,0:11:09.70,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Cool!  The buildings are growing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.98,0:11:28.48,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,This city is a fortress, designed\Nto protect from the Angels.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.98,0:11:30.86,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,This is Tokyo-3...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.35,0:11:33.06,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,This is our city.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.12,0:11:38.94,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,And... it’s the city that you saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.31,0:11:54.98,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Your things should have already\Nbeen delivered, Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.64,0:11:59.82,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I just moved into this apartment, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.42,0:12:02.12,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.12,0:12:05.76,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Pardon... the intrusion...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.89,0:12:09.93,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Shinji...  this is your home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.73,0:12:18.77,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m...  I’m home...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.27,0:12:20.87,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.47,0:12:25.81,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Um, as you can see, the place is a\Nlittle bit messy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.81,0:12:27.29,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Make yourself comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.21,0:12:30.69,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You call this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.85,0:12:33.19,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...a “little bit” messy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.68,0:12:36.99,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Oh!  Sorry!  Could you put\Nthe food in the fridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.99,0:12:38.43,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Uh... sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.65,0:12:40.66,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Ice...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.16,0:12:42.43,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Snacks...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.06,0:12:44.66,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,And tons of beer...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.33,0:12:47.43,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What kind of a life does she lead?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.44,0:12:57.61,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Excuse me... what’s in the other fridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.61,0:13:01.31,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Oh, don’t mind that.  He’s\Nprobably still sleeping!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.74,0:13:02.78,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.98,0:13:07.08,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Let’s eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.08,0:13:08.36,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Let’s eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.19,0:13:20.76,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Life just doesn’t get any\Nbetter than this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.50,0:13:26.27,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Don’t you want to eat?  It’s good,\Neven if it is all instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.07,0:13:30.74,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m sorry, I’m just not used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.74,0:13:33.55,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,That’s no excuse!  You can’t\Nbe so finicky.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.14,0:13:38.02,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,No... that’s not what I... uh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.75,0:13:40.32,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Isn’t this nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.12,0:13:43.48,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Having two for dinner instead of\Neating alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.48,0:13:45.90,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Uh... yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.49,0:13:49.50,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.50,0:13:51.06,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Let’s go for the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.06,0:13:53.56,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Paper, stone and scissors...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.56,0:13:57.30,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Pon!  Pon!  Pon!  Pon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.93,0:14:00.74,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Sorry, Shinji.
