Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.20,0:14:05.65,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Okay!  That was a pretty fair way of\Nsplitting our daily chores, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.27,0:14:07.28,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:13.19,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,This is your home now, so make yourself\Ncomfortable and take advantage of\Neverything here... except me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.61,0:14:14.95,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Y... yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.95,0:14:18.89,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Man... “Yes, yes, yes”... is that all you\Nsay?  It’s getting on my nerves.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.89,0:14:22.46,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You’re a boy, aren’t you?\NAct like a man!  Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.86,0:14:23.86,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Y... yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.59,0:14:27.77,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Okay, that’s just the way you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.13,0:14:31.13,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well, why don’t you go take a bath and\Nscrub away those bad memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.13,0:14:33.31,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Bathing cleanses both the\Nmind and soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.21,0:14:44.61,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,M... M... Miss Misato!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.61,0:14:45.25,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.25,0:14:47.95,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,A p... p... p...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.52,0:14:49.52,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.22,0:14:53.76,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Oh, him?  He’s one of those new\Nwarm water penguins.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.73,0:15:04.17,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Th... th... that was a what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.17,0:15:07.70,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,His name is Pen Pen.  He’s your\Nother roommate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.40,0:15:10.81,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Why don’t you cover that up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.11,0:15:20.65,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Fade In,{\fad(170,0)}I guess I’m not being as nice\Nas I ought to...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.65,0:15:23.16,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Fade Out,{\fad(0,170)}Of course, he’s probably already made\Nup his mind about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.02,0:15:26.16,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Fade In & Out,{\fad(170,170)}Misato Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.99,0:15:29.07,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Fade In & Out,{\fad(170,170)}She’s not a bad person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.16,0:15:32.33,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Bathing cleanses both the\Nmind and soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.42,0:15:36.77,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Fade In & Out,{\fad(170,170)}But bad memories always seem to\Nfind me when I’m in the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.73,0:15:39.51,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Fade In & Out,{\fad(170,170)}Like my father...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.50,0:15:42.21,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...and Rei Ayanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.41,0:15:47.48,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,So, how was Rei today?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.24,0:15:52.52,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You did see her at the hospital this\Nafternoon, didn’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.48,0:15:55.65,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,She’ll be ready to work again\Nin twenty days.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.65,0:15:59.60,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,By then, we’ll be ready to reactivate\NUnit 00 from cryostasis.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.32,0:16:03.17,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s so hard on these poor children.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.56,0:16:06.49,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,There is no one else who\Ncan pilot the Evas.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.49,0:16:09.06,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,As long as they survive, that is\Nwhat I’ll have them do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.06,0:16:12.77,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,With no regard to what they may want?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.20,0:16:15.20,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Video Edit / Placement,{\pos(360,350)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Shinji’s Lovely Suite
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.66,0:16:23.54,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Video Edit / Placement,{\pos(677,440)}{\an3}{\c&HFFFFFF&}City Junior High School #1\NTransfer Admission\NShinji Ikari
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.99,0:16:35.93,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yeah, after all the horrible stuff he went\Nthrough, I doubt that he’ll pilot it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.66,0:16:39.64,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Maintaining him is part of\Nyour job, Misato.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.43,0:16:43.60,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m just scared.  I don’t know how\Nto deal with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.60,0:16:47.30,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Grumbling already?  It was your idea\Nto take him in, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.30,0:16:48.51,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Shut up!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.70,0:16:54.32,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Fade In & Out,{\fad(170,170)}I was just thinking of Shinji as a tool...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.67,0:16:56.69,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Fade In & Out,{\fad(170,170)}I’m as shameless as Ritsuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.01,0:16:59.66,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Fade In & Out,{\fad(170,170)}We destroyed the Angel...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.15,0:17:02.82,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...so why can’t I be happy about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.12,0:17:07.99,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Fade In & Out,{\fad(170,170)}Another unfamiliar ceiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.65,0:17:14.67,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Fade In & Out,{\fad(170,170)}Of course.  In this whole city, there’s\Nno place that’s familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.63,0:17:17.80,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,This is your home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.13,0:17:22.25,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,Fade In & Out,{\fad(170,170)}Why am I here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.53,0:17:46.23,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The brain case has been damaged!\NExtent of damage unknown!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.23,0:17:47.96,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,We’re having problems\Nmaintaining activation!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.96,0:17:48.93,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Status report!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.93,0:17:51.80,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The Synchrograph is reversing!\NThe pulses are flowing backward!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.80,0:17:53.53,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Break the circuit!  Block it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.53,0:17:54.37,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,We can’t!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.37,0:17:56.44,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s not accepting the signal!\NIt won’t take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.44,0:17:57.87,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,What about Shinji?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.87,0:18:00.07,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,His monitors aren’t responding.\NHis condition’s unknown!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.07,0:18:01.64,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Unit 01’s gone completely silent!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.64,0:18:02.52,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Misato!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.38,0:18:04.61,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,We’ve got to stop this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.61,0:18:07.28,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Abort the operation!  Rescuing the\Npilot is our first priority!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.28,0:18:08.98,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Eject the entry plug!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.98,0:18:11.39,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,We can’t!  It’s completely\Nout of control!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.39,0:18:12.49,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.03,0:18:22.23,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The Eva’s reactivating!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.23,0:18:24.57,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Impossible!  How could this happen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.43,0:18:26.67,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Impossible...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.67,0:18:27.84,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,A berserker...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.42,0:18:49.73,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It looks like we’ve won.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.53,0:18:56.84,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,An AT Field!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.33,0:18:59.67,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,No!  As long as the Angel has that\NAT Field up...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.67,0:19:01.58,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...he can’t get near the Angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.64,0:19:05.94,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,The left arm has been\Nregenerated!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.94,0:19:07.08,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.71,0:19:13.35,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Unit 01’s expanding an AT\NField of its own!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.35,0:19:15.78,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s neutralizing the phase space!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.78,0:19:18.09,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,No, not neutralizing, it’s eroding it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:24.63,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Unbelievable!  It went through that\NAT Field so easily...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.74,0:20:10.41,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,No!  It’s going to self-destruct!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.65,0:20:23.65,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Is the Eva...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.43,0:20:34.74,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,That must be the Eva’s...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.33,0:20:36.90,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,...true form.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.77,0:20:45.24,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Circuits reconnected.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.24,0:20:47.68,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Systems restored.  Graphs\Nback to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.68,0:20:49.54,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Pilot life signs, confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.54,0:20:51.38,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Send out the recovery team.  Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.38,0:20:53.22,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Preserving the pilot’s life is\Nour first priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.49,0:21:38.99,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Shinji... can I come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.13,0:21:44.44,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,I forgot to tell you something...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.13,0:21:48.11,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You did a very good thing today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.64,0:21:50.08,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,You should be proud of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.11,0:21:53.02,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Good night, Mister Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.31,0:21:56.41,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hang in there.
