Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.05,0:23:13.62,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,A new life with Misato.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.62,0:23:19.59,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Shinji, who passes his life without\Nhaving himself, would surely never\Nhave a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.59,0:23:24.67,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,But when it’s revealed that he’s a\Npilot, he becomes a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.67,0:23:29.34,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Shinji becomes embarrassed and\None boy bullies him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.80,0:23:32.31,ADV VHS (720 x 480),,0,0,0,,Next episode:\N“The Phone That Never Rings.”
